 poster. This also \"],[2,{\"href\":\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/appearance/video#valid-thumbnail\",\"openInNewTab\":false,\"smoothScroll\":false,\"relValues\":[],\"motionChild\":true,\"nodeId\":\"t9gvWQQj9\",\"scopeId\":\"contentManagement\"},[4,\"a\",null,[5,\"improves SEO\"]]],[5,\".\"]]],[4,\"li\",{\"data-preset-tag\":\"p\"},[4,\"p\",null,[5,\"Keep the “Video” component updated in the “Assets” tab under Components in Framer.\"]]]],[4,\"img\",{\"alt\":\"update indicator in the assets panel of Framer UI\",\"width\":\"800\",\"height\":\"500\",\"src\":\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/8zkKXnA4WAivW0tLtulRCWmjXU.png\",\"srcSet\":\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/8zkKXnA4WAivW0tLtulRCWmjXU.png?scale-down-to=512&width=1600&height=1000 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/8zkKXnA4WAivW0tLtulRCWmjXU.png?scale-down-to=1024&width=1600&height=1000 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/8zkKXnA4WAivW0tLtulRCWmjXU.png?width=1600&height=1000 1600w\",\"className\":\"framer-image\",\"style\":{\"aspectRatio\":\"1600 / 1000\"}}],[4,\"p\",{\"dir\":\"auto\"},[5,\"Our optimizations include:\"]],[4,\"ol\",{\"dir\":\"auto\"},[4,\"li\",{\"data-preset-tag\":\"p\"},[4,\"p\",null,[4,\"strong\",null,[5,\"Lazy loading for videos with posters.\"]],[5,\" Videos are only loaded when close to the \"],[2,{\"href\":{\"webPageId\":\"jBMsYchUe\",\"pathVariables\":{\"tFbD45x0_\":\"viewport\"},\"unresolvedPathSlugs\":{\"tFbD45x0_\":{\"collectionItemId\":\"dbfZKD2jn\",\"collectionId\":\"lElvySKj_\"}}},\"openInNewTab\":false,\"smoothScroll\":false,\"relValues\":[],\"motionChild\":true,\"nodeId\":\"t9gvWQQj9\",\"scopeId\":\"contentManagement\"},[4,\"a\",null,[5,\"viewport\"]]],[5,\", ensuring faster initial load times. For example, a video further down the page loads only when the user is about to see it.\"]]],[4,\"li\",{\"data-preset-tag\":\"p\"},[4,\"p\",null,[4,\"strong\",null,[5,\"Paused playback for out-of-viewport “GIF-like” videos.\"]],[5,\" Muted, looping, auto-p